[2020-03-12 07:21:27.000000 192.130.74.201  - [query->ADMINCITAS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='2020-03-12' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

[2020-03-12 07:55:01.000000 192.130.74.201  - [query->ADMINCITAS] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

, max(c.initials) usuario

, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

[2020-03-12 10:58:38.000000 192.130.74.97  - [query->EDGARDO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='03/11/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='03/11/2020' and b.statfact=3

[2020-03-12 11:03:23.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 11:04:00.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 11:29:07.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '

LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='2020-03-12' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

[2020-03-12 12:51:56.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

[2020-03-12 13:11:22.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 13:11:43.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 13:20:34.000000 192.130.74.120  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 13:40:48.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 13:42:00.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

[2020-03-12 13:51:30.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->MBONILLO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '

, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

       FROM

     INNER JOIN MDocumentos   b ON a.doc = b.codtipodoc

       a.fechafac ='3/12/2020' AND   a.cod_subgrupo = 'CONSULTA' and  a.statfact=3  and d.desTipoTargeta is  not null and a.usuario='mbonillo'

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

[2020-03-12 15:21:10.000000 192.130.74.30  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2

[2020-03-12 15:21:43.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3

[2020-03-12 15:42:59.000000 192.130.74.18  - [query->YFELICIANO] ] SELECT 
       SUM( a.total) monto ,ISNULL ( d.desTipoTargeta , 'EXCENTO') modopago, max(d.codforpa) codforpa  
       FROM  
       VentasDiariasCMACST a  
	   INNER JOIN MDocumentos   b ON a.doc = b.codtipodoc  
	   LEFT JOIN VIEWpagosPRCMA d ON a.numfactu = d.numfactu  
       WHERE

, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '

, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta

[2020-03-12 16:26:20.000000 192.130.74.30  - [query->NORTIZ] ] SELECT  b.codclien
, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac

, a.numfactu
, max(a.coditems) coditems
, 'consulta' tipo
, a.fechafac
, max(b.total) total
, max(c.initials) usuario
, max(e.initials) metodo_pago
, concat(b.codclien, ' ') keypass
, CONCAT(a.numfactu, ' '
, max(c.initials), ' '
, CASE WHEN max(e.initials) IS NULL THEN 'EXO' ELSE max(e.initials) END, ' '
, max(b.total))           disp
, max(b.statfact) statfact
     FROM  cma_DFactura a 
LEFT JOIN  cma_MFactura b ON a.numfactu = b.numfactu 
INNER JOIN loginpass c ON b.usuario = c.login 
LEFT JOIN  Mpagos d ON a.numfactu = d .numfactu AND d .id_centro = 2 
LEFT JOIN  MTipoTargeta e ON d .codtipotargeta = e.codtipotargeta
WHERE        a.coditems NOT LIKE '%ST%' and a.fechafac='3/12/2020' and b.statfact=3
GROUP BY a.numfactu, b.codclien, a.fechafac
